# === Graphify ignore rules ===
# Keep the useful, shareable artifacts under graphify-out/:
#   graph.html            interactive graph
#   graph.json            persistent queryable graph
#   GRAPH_REPORT.md       audit report
#   manifest.json         graph metadata
#   .graphify_analysis.json / .graphify_labels.json   analysis + community labels
# Everything below is machine-local, regenerable, or noise — don't commit it.

# AST / stat cache — large and fully regenerable via `graphify update .`
graphify-out/cache/

# Auto-created dated backup snapshots (e.g. graphify-out/2026-07-10/)
graphify-out/20[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]/

# Label signature (machine-local integrity file)
graphify-out/.graphify_labels.json.sig

# Local memory / reflection scratch, if generated later
graphify-out/memory/
graphify-out/reflections/

# Any raw content Graphify fetches via `graphify add`
raw/

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
